            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;@Ingo What are you talking about? My code can be used to create an array of any type.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/464306/gdejohn&quot; title=&quot;7,212 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;gdejohn&lt;/a&gt;
